@startuml
title Athlete Upload Schedule
actor Athlete
participant "Web App" as WA
participant "API Gateway" as API
participant "App Server" as AS
database "Database" as DB

Athlete -> WA: Upload course schedule
WA -> API: Send upload request
API -> AS: Process upload request
AS -> DB: Save course data
AS --> API: Return success
API --> WA: Return success
WA --> Athlete: Display confirmation
@enduml